First Department,

September, 1956

(September 20, 1956). David Posner et al., Copartners Doing Business under the Name “ Posner and Fingerman ”, v. Sound Steamship Lines, Inc., et al.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs. Concur — Peek, P. J., Breitel, Botein, Rabin and Cox, JJ.
